*Sramota* je što njegov brat nikad ne može da pronađe posao. (It is a shame that his brother can never find a job.)

Njegovo obrazovanje je *sramota* za porodicu. (His education is a disgrace to the family.)

Oni su nas sramno ponizili. (*Sramota* je bila za nas.) (They shamefully humiliated us. It was a shame for us.)

Njegov izgled je *sramota*. (His appearance is a disgrace.)

Njegova izjava je bila *sramota*. (His statement was a disgrace.)